        "responseBody": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\n  <title>Financial Sentiment Analysis</title>\n\n  <style>\n    * {\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n\n    body {\n      min-height: 100vh;\n      margin: 0;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      justify-content: center;\n      padding: 24px;\n      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n      color: #172033;\n      background:\n        radial-gradient(circle at top left, #dbeafe 0, transparent 35%),\n        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #ddd6fe 0, transparent 35%),\n        #f5f7fb;\n    }\n\n    .page {\n      width: 100%;\n      max-width: 760px;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n      margin-bottom: 28px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .eyebrow {\n      margin-bottom: 12px;\n      color: #4f46e5;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      letter-spacing: 2px;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n\n    h1 {\n      margin: 0 0 14px;\n      font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 54px);\n      line-height: 1.05;\n    }\n\n    .subtitle {\n      max-width: 620px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      color: #64748b;\n      font-size: 17px;\n      line-height: 1.7;\n    }\n\n    .card {\n      padding: 36px;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);\n      border-radius: 24px;\n      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\n      box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.14);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n    }\n\n    label {\n      display: block;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n      font-size: 15px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n    }\n\n    .input-wrapper {\n      display: flex;\n      gap: 12px;\n    }\n\n    input {\n      width: 100%;\n      min-width: 0;\n      padding: 17px 18px;\n      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      outline: none;\n      font-size: 17px;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      transition: 0.2s ease;\n    }\n\n    input:focus {\n      border-color: #6366f1;\n      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);\n    }\n\n    button {\n      min-width: 180px;\n      padding: 17px 24px;\n      border: 0;\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      color: white;\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);\n      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25);\n      cursor: pointer;\n      font-size: 16px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;\n    }\n\n    button:hover {\n      transform: translateY(-2px);\n      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.32);\n    }\n\n    .features {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n      gap: 14px;\n      margin-top: 26px;\n    }\n\n    .feature {\n      padding: 16px;\n      border-radius: 15px;\n      color: #475569;\n      background: #f8fafc;\n      font-size: 13px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .feature strong {\n      display: block;\n      margin-bottom: 5px;\n      color: #1e293b;\n    }\n\n    .note {\n      margin-top: 22px;\n      color: #94a3b8;\n      font-size: 12px;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 650px) {\n      .card {\n        padding: 25px;\n      }\n\n      .input-wrapper {\n        flex-direction: column;\n      }\n\n      button {\n        width: 100%;\n      }\n\n      .features {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <main class=\"page\">\n    <header class=\"header\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\">Multi-Agent Financial Intelligence</div>\n\n      <h1>Financial Sentiment Analysis</h1>\n\n      <p class=\"subtitle\">\n        Enter a stock ticker to analyze recent SEC filings and financial\n        news using two cooperating financial-analysis agents.\n      </p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"card\">\n      <form\n        method=\"POST\"\n        action=\"http://localhost:5678/webhook/financial-analysis-result\"\n      >\n        <label for=\"ticker\">Stock ticker</label>\n\n        <div class=\"input-wrapper\">\n          <input\n            id=\"ticker\"\n            name=\"ticker\"\n            type=\"text\"\n            placeholder=\"For example: MSFT\"\n            maxlength=\"10\"\n            autocomplete=\"off\"\n            required\n          >\n\n          <button type=\"submit\">\n            Analyze Stock\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </form>\n\n      <div class=\"features\">\n        <div class=\"feature\">\n          <strong>SEC Filings</strong>\n          Analysis of official 10-K, 10-Q and 8-K reports\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"feature\">\n          <strong>Financial News</strong>\n          Recent Marketaux and Finnhub coverage\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"feature\">\n          <strong>Senior Review</strong>\n          Independent review and final sentiment\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"note\">\n        This system provides an automated research summary and does not\n        provide investment advice.\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n</body>\n</html>",
